Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasumi, for how long are you gonna sleep? \NGet up soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Always interrupting it \Non the most interesting spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm awake, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! I'm in my third year of middle school. Kurizawa Kasumi. {no clue what's first part of ***zawa}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A maiden born on September 18th. \NBlood type - A.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! But just because I have A type blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you shouldn't assume \Nthat I'm a serious and tough type myself!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? The boy I've seen in my dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't quite make out his face yet.{guess} Mama just keeps interrupting it at the most interesting moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I hope it becomes true one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's it! {no clue what's "decided"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I prepared toasts for you. {/fried/baked?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the cheerful looks? \NYou dreamt about having a date again?{}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how far did you advance today? Did you kiss him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a dream! A dream! \NThe maiden's aspirations. First fantasies - kiss! {no clue what's "first's daydream; fantasy; fancy; vision"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:07:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my, Kasumi. \NYou shouldn't confuse dreams and reality. {/think together about ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you spend your morning driveling, \Nyou'll be late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Hold it, you! Aren't those mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let me borrow them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't! Those are the high-tech fashion! {No clue how shoes can be high-tech but i've no clue what else haiteku can be here}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not, just this once?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 8 o'clock already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you get there in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be alright, because...{}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, why does this happen every time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say I didn't warn you{ when you're late}!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Yoshiko!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey-hey, did you do your English homework today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you can be sure of that! In my highly admired teacher's class, I can't afford embarrassing myself! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll have to ask for a favor as usual...{}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You haven't done your homework again? \NDon't say I didn't warn you!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on! On the way home, \NI'll buy you some orange juice or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just please let me peek into your notebook! {g, no clue what's uchisasete}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... How about you try one more time?{no clue what's koe}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what would you say \Nto eating french fries together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! I'm taking it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The school that I attend is a middle school \Nfor girls only, attached to a university!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a ton of friends here, \Nso every single day I'm as happy as I can get!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it's after school when I get even more fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"Youth spent on the court..." \NIs not exactly my cup of tea. {tlc, no clue about a single part of this, what to make of kakeru, what's the word after it, what to make of kusai}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it always feels great to work up a good sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:59.50,Sign,,0,0,0,,Zetattelia {parody of Lotteria}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And after tennis, I usually go with my friends \Nto the Zetattelia to grab a bite. {g, no clue what's this zenomi, no clue what to make of demotte}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Michael J. Fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I'm a huge fan of his!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This photo is simply irresistible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You should see how tough I acted the other day! \NI told them "Leave this to me!" {}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he just stare right at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can also play just a tiny bit of piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When playing it, I imagine myself \Nin the middle of a huge meadow.{wide plain or field}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a wonderfully pacifying feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I love all kinds of flowers -
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,like lilac or sweet pea. And soaproot too! {common gypsophila (Gypsophila elegans); baby's breath; babies' breath; soaproot​}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, when the spring \Nis drawing near, I'm always full of beans!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right. \NIf we're talking about things I like - animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Prairie dogs and sea otters are my favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When I look at all these fluffy \Nand cute animals, the time flies by!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want a boyfriend who'd embrace me \Nkindly like this. Who'd be like a big brother to me!{no clue why she brings it up out of the blue and what to make of konna}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, I won't be oversleeping in the morning ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be waking up like clockwork, \Nwanting to see him sooner!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to introduce my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, her habit of occupying the phone for hours on end is a constant source of irritation for mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, for me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Miki? What's going on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry. Kasumi interrupted me. \NI'll call you some other time.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, what's wrong with you, Kasumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your long calls inconvenience everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:12:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, how would we know \Nif a boy decides to dial me? {}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose you mean the guy from your dream? \NYou gave him your number already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean when a boy \Nstares at a girl for a long time? {actually "at what kind of times do boys stare at girls" but that'd kinda mouthful}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? Sid something happen, after all? Do tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I made eye contact \Nwith some boy I didn't know at Zetattelia today...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be... Oh, cut it!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Kasumi always gets carried away like this, \Nshe won't get a boyfriend even in a thousand years!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:13:02.18,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Miki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I want to tell you a couple of things about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:09.31,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... I'm a second year student \Nin a high school for girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:16.71,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Libra born on October 5th.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My blood type is O.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:24.07,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You unruly thing! \NWhat are you thinking of? {no clue what to make of "stubborn person; bonehead; bullethead; pig-headed person" maybe she's not even referring to the guy}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:32.56,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:33.98,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Today as well, in the refreshing sea breeze and dazzling morning sun, I'm off to enjoy myself!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:39.36,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:43.11,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's how I would've preferred it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In the morning, same as everyone else, \NI take the train to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But this daily jolting in an overcrowded train \Nis already driving me crazy!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not to say I dislike the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's kinda how it goes time and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My preference for free time is swimming in the pool. {no clue what's fuu/funi/fugi here, could be hi?} \NI really like this feeling of being completely relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stylishness is the girl's privilege! {dressing (oneself) up; dressing smartly; dressing nicely; making oneself look attractive}\NI can be pretty finicky about it. {no clue what she means by "pretty noisy"}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you never know who'll see you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't afford appearing unsightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I also like wandering through the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Being surrounded by a lot of people \Nis somehow reassuring for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I really am a people person.{lonely person; someone who easily succumbs to loneliness}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I also want you \Nto look at me at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, when wandering around alone, \NI wind up at all sorts of stores.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But because my pocket money is rather tight, \NI don't go beyond looking at goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I wonder if there's ever a good person, \Nwho'd buy me everything I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting carried away a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Get this! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I also watch movies pretty often.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't ever miss the love story flicks. {without fail; diligently; without missing a single}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I'm quite a bit of a romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no good! What should I do \Nif I end up being unable to sleep at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can do this, I don't mind \Nwatching horrors sometimes too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems, I can do reasonably well in sports, \Nso I don't try to push myself too hard. {/do anything special}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't particularly fancy being all sweaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had to choose, I'd rather be fashionable, \Nalways on the forward edge of trends.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wearing things that suit me.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, there's just this one thing I'm so passionate about right now, it's embarrassing, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you alone? \NFancy drinking some tea with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel lonely \Nplaying this arcade all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing... {nc, nani?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Go, go! That way! Good!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm head over heels \Nfor video games these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I know it's embarrassing, \Nit's just not something I could stop doing!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I completely forgot about Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my best friend and we're really close-knit!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She's light-hearted, but despite that, \Nstill considerably smart and fun to hang out with.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! This wasn't on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, even if her clumsiness \Nis embarrassing sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I super-enjoy being around her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, introduction time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.28,0:20:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Shoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki and I were classmates in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We both love the sea a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But while Miki says she likes the summer sea the most, \Nmy choice is the autumn sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As I walk along the ocean at dusk, \Nbathing in the gentle sunlight...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?{doshio?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:42.59,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:49.83,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:56.69,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My birthday is on December 10th.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If we believe what my mom says,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it was snowing heavily on the day I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:21:02.38,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps that is why I'm so fair-skinned?{fair-skinned; light-complexioned}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:09.84,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also a member of the cheerleading club.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My school has a very active sports division, \Nso we're a mighty busy club.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In summer, it's hot, but we have to shout loudly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In winter, it's cold, but we still have to bare our legs. \NI can't stand it, honestly!{unsure, maybe she means "swing legs around"}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end, the match \Nis what matters the most, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When I see someone downcast, \Nor a child who doesn't look cheerful,{}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't help cheering on them more and more!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, nobody likes the depressed people!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.95,0:22:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Everyone is cheerful after all! \NBeing cheerful is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.79,0:22:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You there, are you fretting over something? {worriedly; (fretting) constantly; (worrying) over this and that; (obsessing) to no end​}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll cheer you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right. I go shopping in my free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.11,0:22:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Toy stores are my favorite!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it's childish?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.28,0:22:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I'm also an avid reader.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.84,0:22:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Be it Tanith Lee, or Ohara Mariko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.58,0:22:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm going through Salinger's \Nthe Catcher in the Rye​.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll also let you sneak a peek \Nat this dream of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me! Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.97,0:23:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.92,0:23:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.53,0:23:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What's going on? This guy is definitely weird.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.92,0:23:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.59,0:23:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I love strong and sturdy guys \Nwho step in to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.39,0:24:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You, who I made fun of, \Nyou'll protect me, won't you?{}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right, right! Here's my another best friend - Pal.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.84,0:24:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still a cute little kitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.01,0:24:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Pal? You want to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.67,0:24:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, try to catch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.66,0:24:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.60,0:24:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.29,0:24:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pal, get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.41,0:24:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What a mischievous child you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.58,0:24:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.70,0:24:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.26,0:24:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A very bad guy looking to disrupt the peace on earth!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.91,0:24:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.21,0:24:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.13,0:24:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.25,0:24:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I guess it'll be a while \Ntill I get a boyfriend if I keep acting like this.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.89,0:24:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I hope you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.91,0:25:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to fall in love too!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.57,0:25:14.55,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.46,0:25:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, enough of that already, Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.54,0:25:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.55,0:25:18.51,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.76,0:25:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Miki is the funniest when she does that! {nc}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.50,0:25:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Because now she would really start doing it! {still no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.56,0:25:28.61,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.70,0:25:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I hearing from our dear Kasumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.03,0:25:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, what I want is a kind boyfriend \Nwho'd be like big brother to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.26,0:25:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Miki?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.01,0:25:39.84,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.45,0:25:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't stand for it \Nif he's just kind and nothing more.{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.12,0:25:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I need someone who'd comply with my whims, \Nbut would still scold me when I'm in the wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.30,0:25:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd hate to hang out with someone so mundane. {/ordinary}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.84,0:25:50.50,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.18,0:25:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You may think it's a bit whimsical, \Nbut I'd like a superhero.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.12,0:25:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.45,0:25:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, someone sturdy \Nand with a strong sense of justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.49,0:25:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, you're watching too much TV! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.75,0:25:54.55,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.22,0:25:59.41,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.22,0:26:13.34,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.54,0:26:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.26,0:26:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that help you understand our hearts?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.10,0:26:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd like to know us better... {lit: if you like us this way [go buy SRM game or something]}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.16,0:26:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.59,0:26:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be waiting for you in the game! {/see you in the game next time}
