Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.96,0:28:16.42,Sign,,0,0,0,,Bonus scene! \N🖤Kasumi🖤Miki🖤Shoko's Super HD Mahjong: Part 1
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.94,0:28:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.65,0:28:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.90,0:28:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting pretty tired of playing strip mahjong.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.95,0:28:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, do I have some news to ease your grief...{no clue what sh emeans by "to such a lamenting you"}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.41,0:28:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.22,0:28:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally out!{unsure, could be question?}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.88,0:28:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The ultimate mahjong!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.95,0:28:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Boasting endless progression, \Nthe latest Super Real Mahjong!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.40,0:28:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a hidden pitfall to this? {no clue what sh emeans, assumed "this seems wrong somewhere"}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.67,0:28:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.34,0:28:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! You're so strong in this game!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.22,0:28:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But you still have some more layers to go through! {no clue waht she means "it seems, I'm that overlapping; piling; stacking"}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.49,0:28:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So? So? Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.35,0:28:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't make any sense! {lit: don't do meaningless things}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.40,0:29:00.86,Sign,,0,0,0,,Bonus scene! \N🖤Kasumi🖤Miki🖤Shoko's Super HD Mahjong: Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.62,0:29:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander! Our forces are wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.40,0:29:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A-At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.08,0:29:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to end this all with a harakiri!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.83,0:29:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too early for that!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.57,0:29:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have something more to do before you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.95,0:29:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.66,0:29:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,After I kill my sister, I can die myself!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.39,0:29:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.23,0:29:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it with rash decisions! {nc what's machuu, assumed matte}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.09,0:29:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fret! We'll just use our army's ultimate weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.59,0:29:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Surely, you can't mean {\i1}that{\i0}... {}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.44,0:29:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.14,0:30:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da! {}
